## Non-negotiable rules

| Rule | Detail |
|:---|:---|
| TypeScript strict | No `any`, no ESLint disables |
| Multi-tenancy | Every DB table: `tenant_id`; every query scoped by tenant |
| RBAC | Every endpoint: `@Permissions('module.resource.action')` |
| Change history | Every mutation: `@TrackChanges` + `ChangeHistoryInterceptor` |
| Module isolation | No cross-module imports; use domain events |
| UI design system | `@unerp/ui` + `.frappe-*` classes only; no inline styles; no hardcoded colors |
| Logging | `@unerp/shared/logger` only; never `console.log` |
| Secrets | Env vars only; never in code |
| Migrations | `pnpm db:migrate` only; never hand-edit `prisma/migrations/` |
| Test coverage | 80%+ on all business logic |
| Breadcrumbs | Every UI page; register segments in `SEGMENT_NAMES` in layout.tsx |

